len muss.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aBrundtlandbericht. 4aClub of Rome. 4aNachhaltigkeit. 4aadditive und integrierte Umwelttechniken. 4aumweltökonomische Gesamtrechung. 7aBUSINESS & ECONOMICS / Economics / General.2bisacsh1 aJörg, Andrea, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Business and Economics 2000 - 2014z9783110635737oZDB-23-GBE08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruyterteBook-Paket OWV/AV  BWL, VWL 2005-2012z9783110345650oZDB-23-OAV0 cprintz978348671803440uhttps://doi.org/10.1524/978348671898040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783486718980423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783486718980/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GBEc2000d2014  aZDB-23-OAVc2005d2012